&lt;p&gt;At the same time, you will be AccuWeather’s primary representative to the &lt;strong&gt;American Meteorological Society (AMS)&lt;/strong&gt;, working to integrate AccuWeather’s subject matter expertise into AMS publications, committees, and major conference programming. You will champion AccuWeather’s presence and thought leadership across the full range of AMS activities.&lt;/p&gt;
