&lt;li&gt;Develop and execute AccuWeather’s Congressional outreach strategy in coordination with senior leadership&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Proactively monitor the legislative and regulatory landscape to identify emerging bills, hearings, and policy developments relevant to AccuWeather and the broader weather enterprise&lt;/li&gt;
