&lt;li&gt;Cultivate and maintain strong relationships with reporters, editors, producers, and influencers across national, business, technology, science, trade, and broadcast media&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Draft, edit, and oversee the distribution of press releases, media advisories, statements, talking points, FAQs, and executive messaging&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Lead proactive media outreach strategy to secure coverage highlighting AccuWeather’s Superior Accuracy™, innovation, thought leadership, AccuWeather For Business solutions, and the AccuWeather Network&lt;/li&gt;
