&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;AccuWeather | Broadcast &amp;amp; Emerging Media Technology&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;AccuWeather is seeking a high-performing, strategic&lt;strong&gt; Senior Account Executive&lt;/strong&gt; to lead sales for &lt;strong&gt;ImmersiCast™&lt;/strong&gt;, our revolutionary next-generation weather presentation platform transforming broadcast television through immersive augmented reality. This is not another weather graphics system. ImmersiCast™ is redefining how television stations communicate weather by combining cinematic augmented reality, advanced visualization, and real-time meteorological intelligence into one groundbreaking platform built specifically for live television. Powered by Unreal Engine and AccuWeather’s industry-leading weather data, ImmersiCast™ enables broadcasters to create unforgettable, immersive weather storytelling experiences that dramatically elevate viewer engagement.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The ideal candidate is an experienced media technology sales leader with &lt;strong&gt;a proven track record selling enterprise broadcast solutions&lt;/strong&gt;, developing strategic relationships with television station groups, and introducing innovative technology to the market.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;About ImmersiCast™&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;ImmersiCast™ catapults weather presentations into the AI- and immersive-media era.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The platform combines:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced augmented reality visualization&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Real-time weather intelligence&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Broadcast-grade rendering technology&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Fully integrated hardware, software, and data services&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Flexible deployment as a standalone system or enhancement to existing weather platforms&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;With ImmersiCast™, meteorologists can step inside storms, interact with weather elements in three-dimensional space, and guide viewers through forecasts in ways traditional presentations simply cannot match.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;From hurricanes and tornadoes to lightning, flooding, and severe weather events, ImmersiCast™ makes complex weather easier to understand, more impactful, and visually unforgettable.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Why This Opportunity Matters&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Every station presents the weather similarly today. ImmersiCast™ gives broadcasters the ability to differentiate themselves in a highly competitive media environment with immersive storytelling technology their competitors may not yet have access to.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;This is an opportunity to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Introduce a category-defining broadcast technology platform&lt;/li&gt;
